import math
for _ in range(int(input())):
    n = int(input())
    l = list(map(int, input().split()))
    g = l[0]
    for i in l:
        g = math.gcd(i, g)
    print(0 if g == 1 else -1)

import math
t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    n = int(input())
    l = list(map(int, input().split()))
    l.sort()
    ans = math.gcd(l[0], l[1] % l[0])
    if ans == 1:
        print(0)
    else:
        print(-1)
